<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6538855">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6538855/" class="title-link">残酷的冰封之战</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6538855"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dongguaming/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3768715-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dongguaming/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">冬瓜明</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-02-07"
      class="main-meta">2014-02-07 21:28:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6538855_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   最好的战争小说是反战的，是对战争的揭露、控诉和反思。《冰封的退路》这本书描写得那么地真实和残酷，“只有沸腾的血，才能融化冰封的莫斯科”，而“冰封的退路”这个名字取得那般地残酷，阅读的过程中，我们仿佛置身到那个冷酷的世界，气温在持续而急剧地降低着，到处都是冻...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6538855_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6538855_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
